examples.en: McKinley was assassinated by a professed anarchist

examples.en: The 20th century has seen too many assassinated leaders.

examples.en: Earthshaking news — the President has been assassinated.

examples.en: Anwar Sadat was assassinated because many people did not like his peace politics with Israel.
